      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，STOP用红色填充，背景浅红、边框深红，一眼就能看出是故障路径。PROCESS节点我注意到名字可能有点问题——它应该还是MQTT Broker，但功能上是处理数据。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PROCESS",
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已调整，PROCESS保持为IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker实例。继续往下，PROCESS之后输出PROCVAL，这里又是一个决策点？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PROCESS",
        "PROCVAL"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "没错，PROCVAL判断处理后的值是否有效。VALID的流向执行器控制器做最终消费，INVALID的走安全模式。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PROCVAL",
        "VALID",
