      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，都是IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController，只是业务场景不同：CONSUME是正常消费执行，SAFE是安全保护状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
